      "content": "i dont even know why i’m still starting new days. everything just feels so heavy. the lab, the funding, the feeling that i’ve wasted years on nothing... it’s like i’m just running a race that has no finish line and i'm too tired to even keep my head up anymore. i’m just so incredibly exhausted. i just want everything to be quiet. i just want the noise to stop.",
