      "content": "the problem is everything is tied to this. my whole identity, my visa, my parents... it's all built on this career. and now it's falling apart. it's not just \"taking a break\" for a weekend. it feels like there's no way to actually get away from it all. the exhaustion is just... it's permanent. it's in my bones. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just stop existing. like, truly stop.",
